Infinite Pieces Clinic Demo — Complete Local Image Assets

Open index.html. Keep the infinite-demo-assets folder beside it.

This package includes stable local demo images for:
- DTT color and shape flashcards, including crescent
- NET visual cards
- TA handwashing and backpack cards
- PRT car/block cards
- Social Story pages
- Visual Schedule cards in cartoon and realistic-style sets
- Transforming Robots and Animals token board presets

No API key is needed for the demo. Production image generation should be backend-only.
